    "The company was set up in 1984 by Chen and other alumni of Taiwan's National Chiao Tung University, including Leo Huang who is also a billionaire.",
    "Chroma's power testing equipment is finding increasing uses worldwide as the AI boom leads to rising electricity usage.",
    "Chen struck out on his own and set up Dynacolor, a Taiwan-listed maker of video surveillance products, in 1991."
